[assistant] What changed functionally:
[assistant] 
[assistant] - The JVM test process now starts with a custom system class loader that rejects only `com.google.common.base.internal.Finalizer`.
[assistant] - This makes `FinalizableReferenceQueue$SystemLoader` naturally fail to load `Finalizer`.
