[assistant]   - `ClassLoader#getResource(...)`
[assistant]   - `ClassLoader#loadClass(...)`
[assistant] - The helper class loader is isolated in a separate source set and appended to the bootstrap classpath so it can be used as `java.system.class.loader`.
